entries.title_d: Hunt down Black Sun throughout the Naboo System.
entries.title: Naboo System: Duty: Devastating attack on the Black Sun
entries.taunt_5: Time to add another RSF puppet on my kill list!
entries.taunt_4: You should never have come here, now you will never leave.
entries.taunt_3: Your about to learn the foolishness of messing with the Black Sun!
entries.taunt_2: Royal Security Force? More like Royally Slow Fools!
entries.taunt_1: I guess not all RSF is on our payroll. No matter, you won't be on anyones payroll after this!
entries.targets_detected: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Vessels fitting hunted ship profile on attack vector, weapon systems armed. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.targets_behind: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Be aware, vessels trying to target this ship with their weapon systems. Attack originating direction 180 degrees. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_location_d: Random sorties throughout the Naboo System.
entries.level_increase: Sensors through out the sectors show increased Black Sun activity in response to our attacks.
entries.level_boss_dead: That one has been a dread ever since he came to this sector, great work pilot!
entries.level_boss: RSF Command: < The Black Sun have sent one of their best pilots to take care of you, be careful! >
entries.found_loc: The next area of known Black Sun activity has been uploaded to your nav computer, proceed when ready.
entries.dd_boss_taunt_5: Your pilot helmet will look good on my trophy rack RSF fool!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_4: Maybe I should fly using just one hand, to give you a chance?
entries.dd_boss_taunt_3: Too bad you ran in to me so early in your career, as I mark it's end!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_2: To us you're just a anuiance, about to be squashed!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_1: Foolish RSF puppet, you should have run while you had the chance!
entries.complete: Fantastic job pilot! We struck a blow to the Black Sun that will take them a long time to recover from. Head back to base when ready.
entries.boss_detected: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Vessel with veteran insignias on attack vector, weapon systems armed. \#pcontrast3 >
